  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Heat the olive oil in the clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the cacao powder, saffron threads, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the uncooked calasparra rice and stir to combine.",
    "Add the vegetable broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the clay pot and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until the rice is tender and the liquid is absorbed."
